title: UK expels Russian diplomats after nerve gas attack
text:
UK expels Russian diplomats over nerve agent attack 2:33pm GMT - 01:45 
The British government unveiled a range of measures it is taking against Moscow - who it blames for the nerve gas poisoning of a former Russian spy on British soil. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
